These packages contain initial published versions of the FSDF models for Thematic Working Groups: - FSDF Administrative Boundary Theme - FSDF Place Names Them

Common models describe key aspects of the FSDF. Key packages are: Context Models - FSDF Core Conceptual Model - a high level description of the FSDF core model - FSDF Domain Model - key FSDF concepts - FSDF Modelling - process and use case models for the modelling initiative - FSDF Governance - initial draft of proposed FSDF governance structure and roles.
